  <brief_title>Receptor Occupancy of ITI-007 Using Positron Emission Tomography (PET) in Patients With Stable Schizophrenia</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label Positron Emission Tomography (PET) Study to Demonstrate Receptor Occupancy, Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacokinetics of ITI-007 in Stable Schizophrenia Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
